UBS CEO Says He Still Has Confidence of the Board, Reuters Says

-- B y   L a r s   K l e m m i n g
-- 
2011-09-21T00:26:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/ubs-ceo-says-he-still-has-confidence-of-the-board-reuters-says.html
UBS AG (UBSN)  Chief Executive Officer
 Oswald Gruebel  told reporters in Singapore today that he’s still
confident of having the board of directors’ support, Reuters
reported, citing the executive.  Gruebel is in Singapore in connection with a board meeting
this week where strategic changes to the investment bank are on
the agenda, the report said, citing several unidentified people
with direct knowledge of the plans.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Lars Klemming at 
 lklemming@bloomberg.net  